sequenceDiagram
    participant CLI as CLI Orchestrator
    participant PRContext as PR Context
    participant GitHubAdapter as GitHub Adapter
    participant WriteQueue as Write Action Queue
    participant GitHub as GitHub API
    participant Manifest as Manifest/Artifacts

    Note over CLI,Manifest: PR Creation Flow (ai-feature pr create)

    CLI->>PRContext: Load PR context
    PRContext->>Manifest: Read manifest.json
    Manifest-->>PRContext: Return manifest
    PRContext->>Manifest: Check approvals
    alt Code approval missing
        Manifest-->>CLI: Error: Code gate not approved
        CLI-->>CLI: Exit 30 (human action required)
    end
    PRContext->>Manifest: Check validation.json
    alt Validations failed
        Manifest-->>CLI: Error: Validations not passed
        CLI-->>CLI: Exit 30 (human action required)
    end
    PRContext->>CLI: Context loaded

    CLI->>GitHubAdapter: Create adapter instance
    GitHubAdapter->>GitHub: Validate token & credentials
    GitHub-->>GitHubAdapter: Token valid

    CLI->>GitHubAdapter: createPullRequest(params)
    GitHubAdapter->>GitHub: POST /repos/{owner}/{repo}/pulls
    Note right of GitHub: Rate-limit check<br/>before request
    GitHub-->>GitHubAdapter: PR created (number, url, etc)
    GitHubAdapter-->>CLI: Return PR metadata

    alt Reviewers requested
        CLI->>WriteQueue: Queue reviewer request
        WriteQueue->>GitHubAdapter: requestReviewers(params)
        GitHubAdapter->>GitHub: POST /pulls/{number}/requested_reviewers
        Note right of GitHub: Rate-limit check<br/>before request
        GitHub-->>GitHubAdapter: Reviewers requested
        GitHubAdapter-->>WriteQueue: Success
        WriteQueue-->>CLI: Action queued
    end

    CLI->>Manifest: Persist pr.json
    Manifest-->>CLI: Saved
    CLI->>Manifest: Update feature.json external_links
    Manifest-->>CLI: Updated
    CLI->>Manifest: Log deployment action
    Manifest-->>CLI: Logged to deployment.json
    CLI-->>CLI: Output PR URL & details

    Note over CLI,Manifest: PR Status Check Flow (ai-feature pr status)

    CLI->>PRContext: Load PR context
    PRContext->>Manifest: Read pr.json
    Manifest-->>PRContext: Return PR metadata

    CLI->>GitHubAdapter: getPullRequest(pr_number)
    GitHubAdapter->>GitHub: GET /repos/{owner}/{repo}/pulls/{number}
    GitHub-->>GitHubAdapter: PR details
    GitHubAdapter-->>CLI: Return PR

    CLI->>GitHubAdapter: getStatusChecks(head_sha)
    GitHubAdapter->>GitHub: GET /repos/{owner}/{repo}/commits/{sha}/check-suites
    GitHub-->>GitHubAdapter: Status check suites
    GitHubAdapter-->>CLI: Return status checks

    CLI->>GitHubAdapter: isPullRequestReadyToMerge(pr_number)
    GitHubAdapter->>GitHubAdapter: Evaluate merge readiness
    Note right of GitHubAdapter: Check:<br/>- PR state (open)<br/>- Draft mode<br/>- Mergeable<br/>- Status checks<br/>- Branch protection
    GitHubAdapter-->>CLI: Return {ready, reasons[]}

    alt Blockers present
        CLI->>CLI: Build blocker list
        Note over CLI: Blockers:<br/>- Status checks failed<br/>- Required reviews missing<br/>- Branch protection rules<br/>- Merge conflicts
    end

    CLI->>Manifest: Update pr.json with fresh data
    Manifest-->>CLI: Saved
    CLI-->>CLI: Output merge status & blockers

    Note over CLI,Manifest: Reviewer Request Flow (ai-feature pr reviewers)

    CLI->>PRContext: Load PR context
    PRContext->>Manifest: Read pr.json
    Manifest-->>PRContext: Return PR metadata

    CLI->>WriteQueue: Queue reviewer request
    WriteQueue->>GitHubAdapter: requestReviewers(params)
    GitHubAdapter->>GitHub: POST /pulls/{number}/requested_reviewers
    Note right of GitHub: Rate-limit check<br/>before request
    GitHub-->>GitHubAdapter: Reviewers requested
    GitHubAdapter-->>WriteQueue: Success
    WriteQueue-->>CLI: Action completed

    CLI->>Manifest: Update pr.json reviewers list
    Manifest-->>CLI: Saved
    CLI->>Manifest: Log to deployment.json
    Manifest-->>CLI: Logged
    CLI-->>CLI: Output updated reviewers

    Note over CLI,Manifest: Auto-Merge Control Flow (ai-feature pr disable-auto-merge)

    CLI->>PRContext: Load PR context
    PRContext->>Manifest: Read pr.json
    Manifest-->>PRContext: Return PR metadata

    alt Auto-merge already disabled
        CLI-->>CLI: Exit early (no-op)
    end

    CLI->>WriteQueue: Queue auto-merge disable
    WriteQueue->>GitHubAdapter: disableAutoMerge(pr_number)
    GitHubAdapter->>GitHub: POST /graphql (DisableAutoMerge mutation)
    Note right of GitHub: GraphQL mutation:<br/>disablePullRequestAutoMerge
    GitHub-->>GitHubAdapter: Auto-merge disabled
    GitHubAdapter-->>WriteQueue: Success
    WriteQueue-->>CLI: Action completed

    CLI->>Manifest: Update pr.json (auto_merge_enabled: false)
    Manifest-->>CLI: Saved
    CLI->>Manifest: Log governance note to deployment.json
    Note over Manifest: Record reason<br/>for disabling<br/>auto-merge
    Manifest-->>CLI: Logged
    CLI-->>CLI: Output confirmation

    Note over CLI,Manifest: Write Action Queue & Rate Limiting

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over WriteQueue: Write Action Queue serializes<br/>all write operations (comments,<br/>reviewers, labels, auto-merge)<br/>to prevent GitHub abuse detection
        WriteQueue->>WriteQueue: Check queue backlog
        alt Queue backlog high
            WriteQueue->>WriteQueue: Wait for drain
            Note over WriteQueue: Observability hub alerts<br/>operators if backlog grows
        end
        WriteQueue->>GitHubAdapter: Execute next action
        GitHubAdapter->>GitHub: API call with rate-limit headers
        GitHub-->>GitHubAdapter: Response + rate-limit info
        GitHubAdapter->>GitHubAdapter: Update rate-limit ledger
        alt Rate limit approaching
            GitHubAdapter->>WriteQueue: Throttle signal
            WriteQueue->>WriteQueue: Increase inter-request delay
        end
        WriteQueue->>Manifest: Persist queue state to disk
        Note over Manifest: Enables resume after crash
    end

    Note over CLI,Manifest: Branch Protection Feedback Loop

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        CLI->>GitHubAdapter: isPullRequestReadyToMerge(pr_number)
        GitHubAdapter->>GitHub: GET /repos/{owner}/{repo}/pulls/{number}
        GitHub-->>GitHubAdapter: PR details (mergeable_state: blocked)
        GitHubAdapter->>GitHub: GET /repos/{owner}/{repo}/commits/{sha}/check-suites
        GitHub-->>GitHubAdapter: Failed status checks
        GitHubAdapter-->>CLI: {ready: false, reasons: ["Status checks failed", "Required reviews missing"]}
        CLI->>Manifest: Record failing contexts
        Manifest-->>CLI: Saved to pr.json
        CLI-->>CLI: Surface blockers to user
        Note over CLI: User resolves blockers<br/>manually or via re-run
        CLI->>CLI: Retry status check
        CLI->>GitHubAdapter: isPullRequestReadyToMerge(pr_number)
        GitHubAdapter->>GitHub: GET /repos/{owner}/{repo}/pulls/{number}
        GitHub-->>GitHubAdapter: PR details (mergeable_state: clean)
        GitHubAdapter-->>CLI: {ready: true, reasons: []}
        CLI-->>CLI: Proceed with merge
    end
